        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title fade-in">Technical Implementation</h2>
            <div class="fade-in">
                <p style="text-align: center; font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 40px; opacity: 0.9;">
                    The Sundew Algorithm implements three-phase processing inspired by carnivorous plant behavior
                </p>
                
                <div class="code-preview">
                    <code>
class SundewAlgorithm:<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;def process_input(self, input_data):<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;# Phase 1: Event Gatekeeper (Low Energy)<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;significance = self.evaluate_significance(input_data)<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if significance < self.threshold:<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;self.maintain_dormancy()  # Stay asleep<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return None<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;# Phase 2: Selective Activation<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;self.activate_processing()<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;# Phase 3: Deep Neural Processing<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return self.deep_process(input_data)
                    </code>
                </div>
                
                <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;">
                    <strong>Mathematical Foundation:</strong> S(t+1) = H(œÉ(x(t)) - Œ∏)<br>
                    Where H is Heaviside function, œÉ is significance function, Œ∏ is adaptive threshold
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

